{"tid":685861,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"高速公路上跑步被撞   老婦四肢「揉成一團」噴飛　","createTime":"2018-05-31T18:12:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-09T22:34:27.000Z","uid":48582,"like":302,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":124,"replies":[{"pid":"1e743b7f0d8b5e3ccb878f43f48d8651f40d65ed","tid":685861,"uid":48582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T18:12:09.000Z","msg":"支那貴州遵義市29號發生一宗高速公路事故，畫面相當駭人。當時一對老夫婦諗住行捷徑去山上取水<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，選擇自殺式橫越高速公路<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，呀婆冇注意到有車嚟緊，成個人直接被部車撞飛2、3公尺<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，連身軀和四肢扭曲成一團慘變真正廢老，讓許多人看完直呼太驚悚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n當天駕駛開車行駛在高速公路上，沒想到右前方突然有一名老婦小跑步竄出，他被右前方鄰車遮蔽視線、反應不及，立刻急踩煞車，但因為車速實在慢不下來，老婦仍被撞飛數公尺。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=g9UAg7E5110\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dg9UAg7E5110&d=fx7eY9BJwtcE%2BbVEeyPzS7%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=73203785\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=g9UAg7E5110</a><br />\n<br />\n老婦被撞飛後，落地前四肢扭曲變形，像是被「揉成一團」。而目睹驚悚畫面的駕駛倒是相當冷靜，當下不僅直呼「快報警」，還下車制止老翁移動老伴，以免造成二度傷害。<br />\n<br />\n老婦送醫治療後，確定有腿部、頸椎及肩椎骨折，所幸並未傷及頭部。事後，老翁坦言，因為想去對面的山上取水，才貪快橫越高速公路，不料卻發生意外。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20180601/1181663.htm#ixzz5H6VXq28a&nbsp;\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20180601%2F1181663.htm%23ixzz5H6VXq28a%C2%A0&d=fx7eY9BJwtcE%2BbVEeyPzS7%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=f1d55153\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20180601/1181663.htm#ixzz5H6VXq28a&nbsp;</a>"},{"pid":"1e2cd2ba1bfcd93719479b8ace14c49d8573ca57","tid":685861,"uid":48582,"like":23,"dislike":28,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T18:13:33.000Z","msg":"有冇人知呀婆死咗未<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b854ca0e2c3f2993